title: Jack Van Impe - Awake America: The World's Final Warning (VIDEO)
description:
The Four Horsemen of the apocalypse are set to ride - and the USA slumbers in ignorance of the catastrophe about to descend upon her! Drs. Jack and Rexella Van Impe desire to awaken this nation to the perils that lie ahead... and soon return of the Savior! Discover the answers to critical questions...

-How soon will apocalyptic judgements begin?

-What does the Bible say about the prediction of the world's end in 2012?

-How do current events fit with prophecies of Christ's coming?

-What is the Mark of the Beast, and who will control it?

-And much more
